3. Internal Use By Companies

Companies and other commercial organizations may use DataPad++ internally for
free. Internal use includes using the official application to connect to,
query, inspect, test, and manage datastores owned or operated by that
organization.

Internal use does not include distributing DataPad++ to customers, clients,
contractors as a deliverable, affiliates as a product, or the public. If you
need redistribution, bundling, managed-service, white-label, OEM, or other
commercial rights, contact FullMontyDevelopment for a separate written
license.

